## Language of free-text labels

Emit free-text labels **English-normalized** whenever a canonical English form
exists (e.g. `"python"`, `"postgres"`, `"project management"`). Keep the value
in its source language only when there is no clean English equivalent
(e.g. `"Mittelstand"`, `"Jobrad"`).

Verbatim fields are different — they are copied from source unchanged. This
rule applies only to fields marked **free-text canonicalizable** in the task.
